{"tid":400541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶) 容祖兒送祖國《祖國兒女》慶祝建國60周年慶典","createTime":"2017-09-15T01:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T02:24:22.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71284d207539d3e375393307d00e88638eedfcd2","tid":400541,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"容祖兒國語專輯【很忙】裏的一首作品《祖國兒女》早在內地cctv現場演唱，原來此曲更是主打之一，宣傳稿更說是容祖兒「為了慶祝建國60周年慶典」而製作，找來金培達作監製。<br />\n<br />\n報紙鱔稿中更指英皇隆重其事，用過百萬製作費拍MV。MV由中央電視台總導演郎昆擔任藝術指導，容祖兒親往長城取景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uEH0k-CVw4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuEH0k-CVw4s&d=RhJcjhBdRSYUKuhesLsMgP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cc1af511\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uEH0k-CVw4s</a>"},{"pid":"0a18afb3d28f7491e0d2d7cdf5dc0e3690bec0fe","tid":400541,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"有一種溫暖 穿透層層心瓣 <br />\n 千里共嬋娟<br />\n 有一種尊嚴 可以世代相傳 <br />\n 任憑滄桑 如何變幻<br />\n<br />\n ＊風雨中堅強的視線 <br />\n 彼此眺望多少年<br />\n 用相同的語言 訴說思念<br />\n 揮別了昨天 攜手向前＊<br />\n<br />\n ＃愛多深 情多濃 都在祖傳血脈中<br />\n 百家姓 一家親<br />\n 祖國兒女永遠都難忘<br />\n 母親的寬容＃<br />\n<br />\n 同一個心願 能把距離縮短 <br />\n 凝成一個圓<br />\n 同一個波段 在空氣中交換 <br />\n 天涯海角 都不遙遠<br />\n<br />\n ＊風雨中堅強的視線 <br />\n 彼此眺望多少年<br />\n 用相同的語言 訴說思念<br />\n 揮別了昨天 攜手向前＊<br />\n<br />\n ＃愛多深 情多濃 都在祖傳血脈中<br />\n 百家姓 一家親<br />\n 祖國兒女永遠都難忘<br />\n 母親的寬容＃<br />\n<br />\n 愛多深 情多濃<br />\n 飛越關山千萬重<br />\n 長城長 紅旗紅<br />\n 祖國兒女的幸福就是 母親的光榮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e6d9231a7c9a39f3845c0f8cf2d0c7523abea5","tid":400541,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"個MV拍成咁值過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101a516bb135bbda94f967f6fbef7152113ee9d6","tid":400541,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個MV拍成咁值過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奶共 ar ma"},{"pid":"725dc38bd8515bc181be10fa34b7da71c8c7ba39","tid":400541,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個MV拍成咁值過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔報大d邊有得貪"},{"pid":"ec77ae79d803d5a00683710f4f137173e88da066","tid":400541,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個MV拍成咁值過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多喇, 你諗下租條船十幾萬, 搭個景再垃圾都要廿萬, 又要飛北京長城, 成TERM人飲飲食食, 100萬好快洗晒"},{"pid":"12c30524321885ccf3089383bdf8d3a03400dec6","tid":400541,"ui